    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200500/extras/9d7d4cbcd12654998362b6ee2d5bd9f0.apng?t=1730550064\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200500/extras/9d7d4cbcd12654998362b6ee2d5bd9f0.poster.avif?t=1730550064\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=190 /></picture></span>You are a travelling potion maker. The land is rich in ingredients. And the heroes need your help! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Potions In Motion is an arcade game based on the classic game Snake with a wholesome theme and unique mechanics that provide new and fun challenges and the potential to achieve really high scores and infinite gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you looking for a challenge? Or would you like to lay back and relax? With three game modes and selectable board sizes Potions In Motion lets you have both. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200500/extras/b2433284abbf78daf1e38b96fc825a4d.apng?t=1730550064\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200500/extras/b2433284abbf78daf1e38b96fc825a4d.poster.avif?t=1730550064\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=64 /></picture></span>Travel around the land and collect the rarest of ingredients: firey phoenix feathers, shimmering pixie dust, elegant buttercup flowers, sparkling sapphires and the fabled black pearls. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a skillful potion maker you can turn these into potions and add them to your ever growing collection. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200500/extras/0f64500f7716d0deae6fc76d24261f04.avif?t=1730550064\" width=616 height=64 /></span>The brave heroes of the land need your help to gear up for their adventures. Deliver them the potions they need and receive rewards that help you reach even higher scores. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You might not face the danger the heroes do, but you still need some rest from time to time. Find the camp fires, slow down to go faster.</p>",
